      "Text": "Security update for polkit",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for polkit fixes the following issue:\n\n- CVE-2026-4897: Fixed possible OOM condition via specially crafted input to `polkit-agent-helper-1` (bsc#1260859).\n",
